{"id":165405,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201174/","date":"2011-07-05T06:00:29Z","modified":"2011-07-08T20:45:53Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/7/4","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110702/wl_nm/us_china_tibet_writer\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国判西藏作家四年徒刑</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">被禁杂志《夏东日》的藏族编辑扎西热丹在四川阿坝被判入狱四年</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/30/world/asia/30briefs-Tibet.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">藏人在四川进行抗议，多人被捕</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——六月间四川发生</span><span>15</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">起藏人抗议事件，至少</span><span>30</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多人被捕</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18832024?story_id=18832024\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">普世主义派与中国特色派的理念之争</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——前者认为中国应该顺应民主大潮，后者坚持中国应该实行专政。目前后者占据绝对上风。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2080808,00.html?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国官员在性丑闻方面不甘人后</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从微博局长，到裸聊主任，还有更早的韩峰日记，中国官员的偷情透露出来的不止是性欲，还有腐败。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">半岛新闻：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://english.aljazeera.net/programmes/101east/2011/06/2011629646319175.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">基督教，中国的最佳选择？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着越来越多中国人信仰基督教，当局对此又高兴又害怕。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>TPM</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://idealab.talkingpointsmemo.com/2011/06/china-grows-its-own-twitter-with-chinese-characteristics.php\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">具有中国特色的</span>twitter</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管新浪微博也受到政府审查，但它仍然推动了中国的公共事务进入一个新纪元</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110705/ts_nm/us_china_debt_moodys\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">穆迪公司称中国地方政府贷款问题比预想的更严重</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——官方公布的统计数字少算了</span><span>3.5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万亿元人民币。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/04/tackling-social-insurance/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国努力解决社会保险</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的社会保险很难理解，因为它除了有经济方面的考虑之外，还受很多政治因素的影响</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hl73xoLXjzjgSlVE_8JWjp58R23g?docId=CNG.34a11628a7892b6c861a8ffb743aafa7.4c1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国媒体称多党制将带来混乱</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国官方媒体称多党制将导致文革式的动乱。但文革时有多党制吗？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18829149?story_id=18829149\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">崛起的实力，不安的国家</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——由于对进一步改革的抵抗势力在不断增加，中国的经济成功面临着威胁。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38129&#038;tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=25&#038;cHash=bb9aecdd5fa45f9d8486dca4f2a4d908\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">马克思主义和资本主义的混合体</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这种做法的后果之一，是党的干部中腐败现象广为流传</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3585\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">红色传统</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——往日的社会主义红色宣传画，现在却成为资本主义世界中的文物。历史开了个大玩笑</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/07/04/what-living-in-china-has-made-me-appreciate-about-america/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">生活在中国让我怀念美国的几个好处</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——没有敏感词；令行禁止；贪腐必惩；允许批评政府</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/04/world/asia/04china.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss&#038;pagewanted=all\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">网上丑闻凸显中国人对国有慈善机构的不信任</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这种不信任的根源，在于政府坚持要控制慈善工作并竭力宣传其庞大的机构。【</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://dongxi.net/b089M\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东西网</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">已有译文】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/05/world/asia/05china.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国慈善丑闻中的关键人物辞职</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中红博爱投资人王军辞职；据称炫富女郭美美是其女友。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国传媒计划：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://cmp.hku.hk/2011/07/02/13543/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡锦涛是否只想拖时间？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他的七一讲话处处流露着在自己任期剩余时间内维持现状的意味</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38128&#038;cHash=392a8b48ab00e17f1294b835dae0cfaf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谁会是中国第一任航母舰长</span>?</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——解放军自</span><span>1987</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年起就选拔海航飞行员进行培训，准备作为航母舰长</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38130&#038;cHash=3d2ee7bc6d71c78d2f51182b7f428f70\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾间谍案显示出中国谍报工作的变化</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——台湾罗贤哲和赖坤�间谍案，显示出中国越来越致力于招募外籍人员为其从事情报工作。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38132&#038;cHash=ad43d187e92b04325eb0d092830397c0\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国成为上合组织轮值主席</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国为上合组织的下一步发展提出了四个目标</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">辛迪加项目：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.project-syndicate.org/commentary/nye96/English\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国应该被“遏制”吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——软实力倡导者约瑟夫・奈表示，对中国的策略应该是“整合兼对冲”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/national-security/china-rebuffed-us-request-to-open-route-for-afghanistan-war-supplies-cables-show/2011/06/30/AG8cdYvH_story.html?tid=sm_twitter_washingtonpost\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">根据外交电报透露，中国拒绝了美国关于为阿富汗提供战争物资通道的请求</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商业内幕：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/congratulations-china-has-abolished-boom-and-bust-2011-7?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29&#038;utm_content=Google+Reader\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国已经消灭了周期性经济危机</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国经济学家刘树成称中国在过去三十年间实现了高位平稳型增长</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/us-firms-look-to-chinas-west-for-growth/2011/06/30/gHQATMxYxH_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国公司到中国西部寻求发展</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着中国东部城市的繁荣和房地产泡沫加剧，许多公司开始到二三线城市寻求机会。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/microsoft-baidu-reach-agreement-for-search-engine-in-china.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">微软与百度加强搜索联盟</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——双方的目标都是</span><span>Google</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。百度用户的英文搜索将由微软的“必应”来提供结果</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/04/researchers-alibaba-yahoo-fight-highlights-threat-to-china-internet-control/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿里巴巴</span>&#8211;<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎之争暴露出对中国互联网控制权的威胁</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——社科院学者在党校刊物上如是说</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/07/when_should_you_deal_with_your_china_ethical_issues_yesterday.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">应该何时处理在中国经营的商业道德问题</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——最佳时机是在进入中国时即作出处理</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/helenwang/2011/07/01/can-groupon-succeed-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">团购网</span>Groupon<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">会在中国取得成功吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——它在中国的起步就没走好，现在不少专家已经宣布它的死刑</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/High-debt-at-Chinese-universities-exposed/articleshow/9098040.cms\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国大学的高额债务曝光</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——到</span><span>2010</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年底，全国</span><span>1100</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">所大学累计债务达</span><span>2630</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿元人民币</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/02/how-china-kills-creativity/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国如何消灭了创造力？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国学校既压力重重又死气沉沉，强迫学生死记硬背以便应付考试。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>BBC</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-13959239\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">房价高昂令中国的中产阶层叫苦</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国投资人可选的金融产品不多，于是很多人将资金投入房市，希望得到高回报</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-ca-china-blockbuster-20110703,0,6297335.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国电影难以打入美国市场</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的票房巨片在美国往往遭遇败绩。张艺谋的新片希望打破这一局面</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110702/wl_asia_afp/chinaminingaccidentcoal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国发生两起煤矿事故</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——上周六广西和贵州发生两起煤矿事故，多名矿工被困井下。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>如果您的iPad可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>即可看到最新译文；如果您的iPhone可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/?m=1\">这里</a>并加入书签；如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5837351745817172998?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":377,"categories":[1],"tags":[10853,8840,10091,17107]}